<![CDATA[<font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Hello&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</font><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">I am contacting you so that we can begin designing your VinSticker. Attached are examples of some of our custom sticker designs. Below are questions that will help us when designing your sticker.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">1. Which example sticker would you like to use as a general layout for your sticker?<br><i><br>If the client has a hi res logo on file:</i></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">2. Attached is the logo we currently have on file. Please verify that it is current. If not, please send your new logo in high resolution format. This is a required format to ensure appropriate print quality.<br><br><i>If the client does not have a logo on file:</i><br><br>2. Please provide a high resolution logo (300 dpi) to print on your custom sticker. This is a required format to ensure appropriate print quality.&nbsp;<br><br>3.&nbsp;<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please verify the following information you wish to display on your VinSticker:</span><br><br><ul><li>Phone Number: {!Account.Phone}</li></ul><br><ul><li>Address: {!Project_Piece__c.Project_Shipping_Address__c}</li></ul><br><ul><li>Website URL: {!Project_Piece__c.Dealer_s_Web_Address__c}</li></ul><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">4. What specific colors would you like us to use, if you have a preference? Please limit to three.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">5. Are there any specific vehicles you would like featured on your sticker? Please provide year, make, and model.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">6. Will you be printing CarFax information? Or do you wish to have a QR Code* on your sticker?</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">*<i>You can only have a QR Code (that prints with the vehicle information) if you have a VinSolution's hosted website.</i></font></div></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br><b><u>Buyer's Guides</u></b></font></div><div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">1. Please confirm that the below address is the correct shipping&nbsp;address:</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">{!Project_Piece__c.Project_Shipping_Address__c}<br><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">2. We will be shipping [NUMBER] of your Buyer's Guides.&nbsp;</font></div></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><font>3. Would you like the Buyer's Guides to be shipped now, or with the Stickers?</font><br><br></font></div>]]></td>
